flowchart TD
    A[PB: Process] --> B[Cortex: Raw Material & Component Storage Optimization]
    B --> C{Is storage optimization successful?}
    C -- Yes --> D[Cortex: Inventory Cycle Counting & Reconciliation]
    C -- No --> E[UI: Notification - Storage Optimization Failed]
    E --> End
    D --> F{Are cycle counts accurate?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Cortex: Obsolete & Excess Inventory Disposition]
    F -- No --> H[UI: Notification - Cycle Counting Failed]
    H --> End
    G --> I{Is disposition plan feasible?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Cortex: Warehouse Slotting & Location Management]
    I -- No --> K[UI: Notification - Disposition Plan Failed]
    K --> End
    J --> L{Is slotting strategy optimal?}
    L -- Yes --> M[Cortex: Material Handling Equipment Maintenance]
    L -- No --> N[UI: Notification - Slotting Strategy Failed]
    N --> End
    M --> O{Is maintenance schedule balanced?}
    O -- Yes --> P[UI: Notification - Process Completed Successfully]
    O -- No --> Q[UI: Notification - Maintenance Schedule Failed]
    Q --> End
    P --> End